metadata.name: Primavera (March, April, May)
metadata.description:
Selected as a top 30 winner for the first @ClaireSilver12 AI competition. 

This work was originally created as part of the AI Weekly Art Challenge by @gracealmera, to illustrate the theme "4 Seasons".

Created in Stable Diffusion, raw render.  
Upscaled using Latent Diffusion.
